sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as ChatController
    participant DB as ApplicationDbContext
    participant AF as AiFallbackService
    participant RasaSvc as RasaChatService
    participant Rasa as Rasa Server

    FE->>API: POST /api/Chat/{sessionId}/messages
    API->>DB: Kiểm tra hoặc tạo ChatSession
    API->>DB: Đọc lịch sử ChatMessage
    API->>AF: NormalizeContextAsync(userId, message, history)
    AF-->>API: normalizedMessage
    API->>RasaSvc: ParseIntentAsync(normalizedMessage)
    RasaSvc-->>API: parsedIntent
    API->>DB: Lưu user message + metadata
    API->>RasaSvc: SendMessageAsync(sender, normalizedMessage, metadataJson)
    RasaSvc->>Rasa: /webhooks/rest/webhook
    Rasa-->>RasaSvc: reply list
    RasaSvc-->>API: assistant replies
    API->>DB: Lưu assistant messages
    API-->>FE: ChatThreadDto
